      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people care but it doesn't change the reality of it. the person in those photos had dreams and a future and a soul. i'm just a hollow shell performing the duties of a human being. it's like i'm just waiting for the clock to run out because there's nothing left to actually live for. it feels like a waste of space just dragging this shell around every day.",
